    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, finished in Grand Prix White. This specimen features the factory-original F22C1 high-revving inline-four engine, mated to a precise, close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is superlative, retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential for exceptional cornering kinematics. The chassis is unmolested, with all factory VIN tags present and no aftermarket modifications. This is a turn-key example of a legendary longitudinal RWD platform, exhibiting pristine compression and seamless VTEC engagement.",
